<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.1.2">
<l>aṇṇalcey  talaikaṭal kaṭaintataṉuḷ</l>
<l>kaṇṇutal nañcuṇṇak kaṇṭavaṉē</l>
<l>viṇṇava ramutuṇa vamutilvarum</l>
<l>peṇṇamu tuṇṭavem perumāṉē</l>
<l rend="indent">āṇṭāyuṉaik kāṇpatō raruḷeṉak karuḷutiyēl,</l>
<l rend="indent">vēṇṭēṉmaṉai vāḻkkaiyai viṇṇakar mēyavaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Making [known] your supremacy, churning the foaming sea,</l>
<l>You who watched as the brow-eyed [one] drank the poison in that,</l>
<l>Our great lord who relished the ambrosia[-like] lady</l>
<l>Who arose in ambrosia as the celestials ate [that] ambrosia,</l>
<l rend="indent">Master, if you bless me with the one blessing of seeing you,</l>
<l rend="indent">I would not want this domestic life, you who dwells in Viṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
